WEBVTT

00:14:30.560 --> 00:14:33.000
This isn't a spectator sport.

00:14:33.800 --> 00:14:37.296
So what's the right answer?

00:14:37.320 --> 00:14:40.896
I don't know. Listen,
I'm no gun control expert.

00:14:40.920 --> 00:14:42.600
I teach the humanities.

00:14:43.800 --> 00:14:45.736
To be human is to learn,

00:14:45.760 --> 00:14:49.856
and to be part of a civilization
is to share your knowledge.

00:14:49.880 --> 00:14:53.416
This kind of honest,
brave and sincere engagement

00:14:53.440 --> 00:14:55.576
is what I ask of my students,

00:14:55.600 --> 00:14:58.656
what I expect of myself as a teacher

00:14:58.680 --> 00:15:01.080
and what I demand of you now.